{"tid":1475751,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完段片, 覺得港元極危險, 是個空心老棺, 隨時玩完","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T05:10:19.000Z","uid":76310,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"058f4071d193fe6e62ace70ae4b18f96d67837d1","tid":1475751,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rb5TxzjwKVw&amp;t=12s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRb5TxzjwKVw%26t%3D12s&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=6fa2fe4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rb5TxzjwKVw&amp;t=12s</a><br />\n睇完段片, 覺得港元極危險, 是個空心老棺, 隨時玩完<br />\n<br />\n我簡略講一講:<br />\n金管局有4個人話事, 他們可以控制4300億美元, 怎樣使用-<br />\n1997: 董建華, 曾蔭權, 許仕仁, 任志剛 <br />\n2014: 梁振英, 林鄭, 曾俊華, 陳德霖<br />\n2018: 林鄭, 陳茂波, 張建宗, 陳德霖<br />\n呢班人做莊, 林鄭, 陳茂波, 張建宗, 陳德霖, 大家覺得佢地信唔信得過?<br />\n<br />\n我知可能有人會話, 無事既, 陳德霖, 信得過既<br />\n但可以告訴大家, 陳德霖將於今年10月1日退休, 親中的證監會副行政總裁梁鳳儀極有機會接班<br />\n而且不要忘記2012年, 7年之前, 689和777已經做莊<br />\n現在金管局, 所謂持有的美元債券, 可能是中国發行的美元債券<br />\n4300億美元: 500億美元需要是現金, 3800億美元可以作投資用途. 簡單來說, 現在可能實際上用來頂住港元只有500億美元. 如果金融大鱷沖衝金融體系的話, 後果相當嚴重. 當然不排除中国會來救香港, 以示港元是穩健安全的. <br />\n<br />\n大家覺得港元危不危險, 自己想<br />\n一聽到話事4人組, 已經覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae2b76f3d9b77b04d2e5c58c9d451dbee946489b","tid":1475751,"uid":204423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:52:45.000Z","msg":"可能係劇本之中。"},{"pid":"1e76c2b737b3d6436f339ef98248d5d2d7f322b2","tid":1475751,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:55:31.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"45496e9373f366a819226e4685ed6286ff5fd528","tid":1475751,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:57:14.000Z","msg":"金管局, 4大話事人-<br />\n2012: 689, 777, 薯片, 陳德霖<br />\n2017: 777, 張建宗, 囤地波, 陳德霖<br />\n一聽完, 覺得外匯, 用作投資果部份肯定比人食晒, 得番實際500億美元<br />\n當然, 我覺得有乜事, 中共都會出黎back up<br />\n所以繼續保持繁榮盛世, 欣欣向榮既表面現象"},{"pid":"1dc719e11a8a710fa9a6b69f826e4f14bdeaffb8","tid":1475751,"uid":220853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"咁咪岩 對準政權<br />\n中共已經內憂外患<br />\n<br />\n內有龐大維穩費<br />\n外有侵侵貿易戰<br />\n再開多條香港戰線<br />\n幾大個水缸都會有流盡既一日<br />\n<br />\n從來都冇一個咁好既和理非群眾運動<br />\n一方面可以保護自己<br />\n另一方面可以痛擊政權<br />\n仲要係完全合法<br />\n<br />\n我唔知你地等乜<br />\n預約換美金啦 宜家 立即"},{"pid":"b7bdc8b40dec57eb993f8a9a2489c05b80d0decb","tid":1475751,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"59e969a5007b32db7096220c41bbc36bf76ec7a6","tid":1475751,"uid":287028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggvtKKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggvtKKe.png&h=95a98f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#816<br />\n#USDchallange<br />\n#光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"7717114030cc1dc5ae1b84f922ad0d012d2cf713","tid":1475751,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59e969a5007b32db7096220c41bbc36bf76ec7a6","tid":1475751,"uid":287028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggvtKKe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggvtKKe.png&h=95a98f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#816<br />\n#USDchallange<br />\n#光復香港時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:09:56.000Z","msg":"美金高咪掃歐羅加紙"},{"pid":"b33d304de21b0151da9a0376aa26ce373518cd40","tid":1475751,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T05:10:19.0